OL,3,CQueen grants Manx capital city status
OL,4,Cas she steps up for King
OL,6,FShe thanked residents for their "warm
OL,7,Fwelcome" before reading out a speech
OL,8,Fprepared by her husband which
OL,9,Facknowledged the late Queen Elizabeth
OL,10,FII.
OL,12,FIt read: "The granting of your city
OL,13,Fstatus is particularly special to me,
OL,14,Fas your Letters Patent are the only
OL,15,Fones in existence that hold both my
OL,16,Fsignature and that of my late mother.
