OL,3,CQueen grants Manx capital city status
OL,4,Cas she steps up for King
OL,6,F"Therefore, ladies and gentlemen, as
OL,7,Fyou mark your well-deserved status as
OL,8,Fone of the newest cities in the
OL,9,FBritish Isles, and the only one of the
OL,10,FCrown Dependencies, I would like to
OL,11,Foffer on behalf of my wife and myself,
OL,12,Fmy heartfelt congratulations and my
OL,13,Fvery best wishes for the future."
OL,15,FQueen Camilla was met with large
OL,16,Fcrowds outside Douglas City Hall, with
OL,17,FHer Majesty meeting many well-wishers
OL,18,Fbefore she was escorted to Government
OL,19,FHouse, in Onchan.
