OL,6,FThe Queen joked about her grandson
OL,7,FLouis being "quite a handful" when she
OL,8,Fmet a baby in the crowd with the same
OL,9,Fname. She said: "I have a Louis
OL,10,Fgrandson... quite a handful".
OL,12,FShe was introduced to a number of
OL,13,Frepresentatives from local charities
OL,14,Fand community groups such as the RNLI
OL,15,Fand the Manx Bluetits swimming club.
OL,17,FDouglas was in May 2022, one of eight
OL,18,Fcommunities in the British Isles to
OL,19,Freceive the honour.
